{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/(main)/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/[level]/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/[level]/page,_N_T_/learn/rag/beginner"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type/$d$level/__PAGE__","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type/$d$level","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type","/!KG1haW4p/learn","/!KG1haW4p","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.0.q-h669a_dqa.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.16t1db8_9y2o~.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0.6dsdn7g3rv..css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14uv9l3-k2qh4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/16sk4~vc8e6sh.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0c9ih0_ge37cg.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-02v2juswviadt.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>RAG 知识库入门教程 - AI工具市场</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"学习 RAG 知识库 的入门知识\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gray-50\"><header class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-3\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-linear-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white text-sm\">⚡</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">AI 工具市场</span></div></a><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"relative w-72\"><div class=\"relative\"><svg class=\"absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-gray-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\"></path></svg><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"全局搜索...\" class=\"w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all\" value=\"\"/></div></div><a class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg transition-colors group\" title=\"学院\" href=\"/learn\"><span class=\"group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">🎓</span></a><a href=\"http://hsinky.cn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg transition-colors group\" title=\"个人博客\"><span class=\"group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">📰</span></a></div></div></header><div class=\"flex\"><aside class=\"w-72 bg-white border-r border-gray-200 flex flex-col fixed left-0 top-14 h-[calc(100vh-56px)]\"><nav class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🏠</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">首页</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">概览与推荐</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/skill\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">✨</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Skill</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">可复用的能力模块</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/mcp\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔌</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">MCP</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">外部工具与服务接入</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/agent\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🤖</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Agent</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">自主决策的AI助手</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/prompt\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">📝</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Prompt</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">高效沟通的模板</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/workflow\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔄</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Workflow</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">多步骤任务编排</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn\">学院</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn/path/beginner\">入门路径</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-gray-900 font-medium\">RAG 知识库</span></nav><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-teal-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-4xl\"></span><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">RAG 知识库</h1><p class=\"text-white/80\">让 AI 知道你的知识</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-white/80 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>预计 <!-- -->80分钟</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>入门路径</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><span class=\"text-gray-500\">难度选择：</span><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-blue-600 text-white\" href=\"/learn/rag/beginner\">入门路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/rag/developer\">开发者路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/rag/architect\">架构师路径</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\"><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">1</span>第一课：为什么需要 RAG？</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-emerald-50 border-l-4 border-emerald-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">核心问题</h3><p class=\"text-gray-700\">大语言模型在公开数据上训练，它不知道你的公司有什么产品、制度、流程。<strong>RAG 让 AI 基于&quot;你的知识&quot;回答问题。</strong></p></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">通用 AI 的局限</h4><div class=\"bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-3\">问普通 AI：&quot;我们公司有什么产品？&quot;</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3\">AI 的回答：</p><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border\"><p>&quot;抱歉，我没有关于贵公司产品的信息。如果您能提供更多细节，...</p><p class=\"mt-2\">或者可能编造：&quot;贵公司可能有电子产品...（幻觉）&quot;</p></div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">RAG 的解决方案</h4><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><span class=\"text-2xl\"></span><p class=\"font-semibold\">RAG = 检索 + 增强 + 生成</p></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"bg-blue-500 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs flex-shrink-0\">1. 检索</span><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">从知识库中找到与问题相关的文档片段</p></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"bg-green-500 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs flex-shrink-0\">2. 增强</span><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">将检索到的内容注入到 Prompt 中</p></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"bg-purple-500 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs flex-shrink-0\">3. 生成</span><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">AI 基于这些内容生成回答</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3 text-blue-700\">类比理解</h4><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">普通 AI</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">= 凭记忆答题</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">遇到没见过的就猜（可能错）</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-green-700\">RAG</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">= 翻书答题</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">根据书上的内容回答（准确）</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2 text-purple-700\">RAG vs 重新训练模型</h4><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\"><p>为什么不直接把公司知识训练进模型？</p><ul class=\"mt-2 space-y-1\"><li>• <strong>成本极高</strong>：训练大模型需要数百万美元</li><li>• <strong>周期长</strong>：从准备到训练需要几个月</li><li>• <strong>难更新</strong>：新内容需要重新训练</li><li>• <strong>RAG 优势</strong>：上传文档即可，立即可用，随时更新</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">2</span>第二课：RAG 完整流程</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">RAG 的五个核心步骤：</h4><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-700\">步骤 1：文档切分（Chunking）</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">把长文档切成小段，便于检索和处理：</p><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm\"><p>原文：&quot;公司成立于2020年，总部位于北京，专注于AI技术研发...&quot;</p><p class=\"mt-2\">切分后：</p><p>Chunk 1: &quot;公司成立于2020年，总部位于北京&quot;</p><p>Chunk 2: &quot;专注于AI技术研发，拥有100+专利...&quot;</p></div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2\">切分策略：固定长度（500字）、按段落、按语义</p></div><div class=\"border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-4\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-green-700\">步骤 2：向量化（Embedding）</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">把每个 Chunk 转换成数字向量，让计算机&quot;理解&quot;语义：</p><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm\"><p>Chunk: &quot;公司专注于AI技术研发&quot;</p><p>→ Vector: [0.23, 0.87, 0.34, 0.91, 0.12, ...]</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 mt-2\">// 这是一个1536维的向量（OpenAI text-embedding-3）</p></div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2\">相似含义的文本会有相近的向量。例如：&quot;AI&quot;和&quot;人工智能&quot;的向量距离很近</p></div><div class=\"border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-purple-700\">步骤 3：索引存储</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">将向量存入向量数据库，支持高效检索：</p><ul class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 space-y-1\"><li>• Pinecone（托管服务）</li><li>• Milvus（开源分布式）</li><li>• Qdrant（轻量高性能）</li><li>• Weaviate（自带向量化）</li></ul></div><div class=\"border-l-4 border-orange-500 pl-4\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-orange-700\">步骤 4：语义检索</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">用户提问时，将问题向量化，在向量数据库中找最相似的 Chunk：</p><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm\"><p>用户问题：&quot;公司有什么产品？&quot;</p><p>→ 问题向量：[0.45, 0.23, 0.67, ...]</p><p>→ 检索结果（Top 5）：</p><p>  1. Chunk 15 (相似度 0.89) &quot;公司产品包括...&quot;</p><p>  2. Chunk 23 (相似度 0.76) &quot;核心业务是...&quot;</p><p>  3. ...</p></div></div><div class=\"border-l-4 border-pink-500 pl-4\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-pink-700\">步骤 5：上下文注入 + 生成回答</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">将检索到的文档插入 Prompt，让 AI 基于这些内容回答：</p><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded text-sm\"><p>Prompt = &quot;基于以下知识回答问题：&quot; + 检索到的文档 + &quot;问题：&quot; + 用户问题</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-cyan-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-cyan-700\">完整流程图</h4><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border text-sm text-center\"><p>📄 文档切分 → 🔢 向量化 → 💾 存储索引</p><p class=\"my-2\">↑</p><p>❓ 用户提问 → 🔍 检索相关内容 → 📝 注入 Prompt → 💬 AI 回答</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">3</span>第三课：向量与语义检索</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">什么是向量？</h4><div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-3\">向量是让计算机&quot;理解&quot;文字含义的关键技术。它把文本转换成一串数字，相似含义的文字会有相近的数字。</p><div class=\"bg-gray-800 text-green-400 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm\"><p>&quot;苹果&quot;（水果） → [0.85, 0.12, 0.34, ...]</p><p>&quot;橙子&quot; → [0.82, 0.15, 0.31, ...]</p><p class=\"mt-2\">// 两者很接近（都是水果）</p><p class=\"mt-2\">&quot;苹果&quot;（公司） → [0.23, 0.91, 0.45, ...]</p><p>&quot;华为&quot; → [0.26, 0.88, 0.42, ...]</p><p class=\"mt-2\">// 两者很接近（都是科技公司）</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-700\">语义检索 vs 关键词检索</h4><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2\">关键词检索（传统）</p><ul class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 精确匹配文字</li><li>• &quot;手机&quot; ≠ &quot;智能手机&quot;</li><li>• 不理解语义</li><li>• 适合：精确字符串匹配</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2\">语义检索（向量）</p><ul class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 基于含义相似度</li><li>• &quot;手机&quot; ≈ &quot;智能手机&quot; ≈ &quot;移动设备&quot;</li><li>• 理解语义关系</li><li>• 适合：模糊查询、同义词</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-green-700\">余弦相似度</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3\">如何计算两个向量有多相似？使用余弦相似度：</p><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-green-600\">相似度 = 1</span><span>→ 完全相同</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-green-600\">相似度 = 0.8</span><span>→ 很相似（如&quot;手机&quot;和&quot;智能手机&quot;）</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-yellow-600\">相似度 = 0.5</span><span>→ 有点关系</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-red-600\">相似度 = 0</span><span>→ 完全不相关</span></div></div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-3\">RAG 中通常选择相似度 &gt; 0.7 的文档片段</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn/path/beginner\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"></path></svg>返回<!-- -->入门路径</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn\">返回学院<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[30824,[\\\"/_n